      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Presenting an exceptional specimen maintained to the highest standards of automotive preservation. This vehicle remains in showroom condition, exhibiting an unblemished exterior and a cabin that retains its original factory integrity. Every mechanical component has been meticulously vetted to ensure peak performance, offering a driving experience indistinguishable from its initial delivery. This is a rare opportunity to acquire an investment-grade vehicle that satisfies the most discerning collector's criteria for excellence.",
